
Generate a buildable source tree (after git checkout)
--------------------------------
autoreconf -v


Check to ensure 'configure.ac' has all checks
---------------------------------------------
autoscan


Create a source tarball (suitable for distribution)
-----------------------
make distcheck


Checkout from sf.net
--------------------
cvs -d:ext:clearscene@opendias.cvs.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/opendias/ checkout opendias
